column10: Field to identify which calls have been accepted or abandoned within 20 seconds
column14:
CASE WHEN Accepted <= 20
		THEN 1
	WHEN Accepted > 20
		THEN 2 
	WHEN Abandoned < 20
	AND Abandoned > 0
		THEN 3
	WHEN Abandoned >= 20
		THEN 4
	WHEN (Abandoned = 0 OR Abandoned IS NULL)
	AND IVRTreatmentTime >= 0
	AND Accepted IS NULL
		THEN 5
			END [Target]

CASE WHEN ([Target] IN ('3', '4')
		AND QueueName = ' ')
			THEN 5
			ELSE [Target]
				END [Target] --- this correct the change that happened to the IVR on 9/7/21
